<p><a href="#sdfootnote4anc" name="sdfootnote4sym">4</a> Robakowski used his window as theme and formal frame for other works during these decades (<em>Bliżej – Dalej </em>[1984] and <em>Samochody, samochody! </em>[1985]).</p>
